dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Warm Springs Mountain quadrangle, Los Angeles County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by Helmut E. Ehrenspeck.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Prepared in cooperation with the California Department of Conservation, Division of Mines and Geology; U.S. Forest Service, Angeles National Forest; and U.S. Geological Survey."
Includes acknowledgments, index to sources of geology, 3 col. cross-sections, and location map.
